  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Snr / Warehouse Supervisor @ Changi South",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Oversee and manage daily warehouse operations to ensure efficiency and accuracy</p></li><li><p>Lead, supervise, and motivate a team of store assistants/storekeepers to achieve departmental goals and KPIs</p></li><li><p>Ensure 100% inventory accuracy at all times</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with HSE rules and regulations across warehouse operations</p></li><li><p>Conduct and chair regular toolbox meetings with the operations team</p></li><li><p>Manage staff matters, including discipline and performance issues</p></li><li><p>Issue warning letters when required</p></li><li><p>Review and approve or reject staff leave applications</p></li></ul><p><strong>Skills & Competencies</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong knowledge of Warehouse Management Systems (WMS), SAP, or other related warehouse applications</p></li><li><p>Proven leadership and people management skills</p></li><li><p>Strong planning and organizational abilities</p></li><li><p>Effective manpower and resource management skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>Experience & Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum of 2 years’ experience in a supervisory role</p></li><li><p>Certificate or Diploma in Logistics & Supply Chain Management or a related discipline</p></li><li><p>Experience in managing a team of 10 or more staff</p></li></ul><p><strong>Working hours (Fixed Shift)</strong><br />Morning shift: 8.00am to 5.45pm<br />Afternoon shift: 1.45pm - 11.30pm (shift allowance $10 per shift per day)<br />Night shift: 11.00pm - 8.45am (shift allowance $15 per shift per day)</p><p><strong>Work Days (Mon - Fri) OR (Thu - Mon), FIXED</strong><br /><strong>Working Location: Changi South(Co. tpt @ AMK, Woodlands, Pasir Ris and Seng Kang)</strong><br /></p><p>Liz Ooi Li Chen (R1104561)<br />Recruit Express Services Pte Ltd (13C6614)</p>",
